	<subsection>
	<title>Explanation Tasks</title>

		<investigation xml:id="pa_rot-07">
		<title>Tipping Truck</title>
		<statement><p></p>
			<p>You observe a truck driving along a road at a constant speed <m>v</m>.  As the truck begins to turn along a flat, circular part of the road, it also begins to tip over.  Use an extended free body diagram to explain why the truck begins to tip.</p>
		</statement>
	</investigation>

